BankAmerica adds non - customer ATM fee . BankAmerica Corp said on Friday that beginning November 17 , it will charge $ 1 . 50 per cash withdrawal by non - customers who use the bank ' s Versateller ATM network in California , Oregon , Washington , Idaho , and Hawaii . It said the fee will not affect Bank of America Versateller cardholders who use the bank ' s ATM network free of transaction charges . The fee will not be charged at many Versateller ATMs at retail outlets , including nearly 500 ATMs in Lucky Stores throughout California . The company operates a total of nearly 7 , 000 ATMs throughout its franchise . 
